[2026-05-18T23:21:09.706Z] [STDOUT] {"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"call_function_jji4jhotnrtr_1","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# Task: 002-browse-02-design\n2\t\n3\t# Design: Browse\n4\t\n5\tGenerate the HTML design mockup for **Browse** using the **Flutter HTML Glossary** constrained vocabulary.\n6\t\n7\t## Critical Constraint\n8\t\n9\tThe HTML MUST use ONLY elements from the **Flutter HTML Glossary** (`stitch-flutter/references/flutter-html-glossary.md`). This ensures the `stitch-flutter` converter can produce pixel-perfect Flutter widgets mechanically.\n10\t\n11\t## Inputs\n12\t- `.stitch/designs/browse/SPEC.md` — Screen specification\n13\t- `.stitch/system/DESIGN.md` — Design system\n14\t- `.stitch/system/META.md` — Reference examples metadata\n15\t\n16\t## Steps\n17\t\n18\t1. **Read spec** — Load `.stitch/designs/browse/SPEC.md` to understand layout, sections, data\n19\t2. **Read glossary** — Load `stitch-flutter/references/flutter-html-glossary.md` to understand the constrained vocabulary\n20\t3. **Select best example match** — Read `.stitch/system/META.md` and score against examples per `stitch-generate/references/selecting-examples.md`\n21\t4. **Read matched reference** — Study the matching example's patterns\n22\t5. **Generate META.md** — Write `.stitch/designs/browse/META.md` with example selection and scoring table\n23\t6. **Generate design.html** — Write `.stitch/designs/browse/design.html` following `stitch-generate` skill using ONLY glossary elements\n24\t\n25\t## Glossary Quick Reference\n26\t\n27\t- Layout: `.column`, `.row`, `.stack`, `.wrap`, `.expanded`, `.padding`, `.sized-box`\n28\t- Scaffold: `.scaffold`, `.app-bar`, `.body`, `.bottom-nav`, `.fab`\n29\t- Text: `.title-large`, `.body-medium`, `.label-small` (Material 3 TextTheme classes)\n30\t- Components: `.card`, `.chip`, `.list-tile`, `.divider`, `.badge`, `.avatar`\n31\t- Buttons: `.elevated-btn`, `.filled-btn`, `.text-btn`, `.icon-btn`\n32\t- Images: