52	## Scrolling & Slivers
53	
54	```html
55	<!-- CustomScrollView with SliverAppBar -->
56	<div data-flutter="custom-scroll" class="flex-1">
57	  <header data-flutter="sliver-app-bar" data-expanded-height="200" data-pinned="true"
58	          class="bg-slate-900">
59	    <img class="w-full h-full object-cover" src="..." />
60	    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Title</h1>
61	  </header>
62	  <div data-flutter="sliver-list">
63	    <!-- list items -->
64	  </div>
65	</div>
66	
67	<!-- Pull to refresh -->
68	<div data-flutter="refresh" class="flex-1">
69	  <!-- scrollable content -->
70	</div>
71	
72	<!-- Safe area -->
73	<div data-flutter="safe-area">
74	  <!-- content -->
75	</div>
76	```
